data.description: RARE OPPORTUNITY to own a home at this price in Staley High School that features a beautiful inground Pool.  This well equipped home also comes with a spacious kitchen, granite counters, breakfast bar, gorgeous backsplash, and lots of cabinet space. Vaulted ceilings. Walkout from the family room to the patio/pool area. Access to the deck/pool area from the kitchen/dining room.  A roomy master bed and bath comes with a walk in closet, granite double vanity, separate shower and whirlpool tub. If that isn't enough, there is a finished subbasement that can be a rec or theatre room.  Plenty of inside and outside storage and a nice level driveway.
